tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  38,49,"This is a reminder of these people through good praise in the Qur’ān. And for the Mindful through carrying out the orders of Allah and refraining from His prohibitions is a good return in the abode of the Afterlife."
  38,58,"And they will have another punishment like this punishment. They will have a number of various punishments they will be punished with in the Afterlife."